These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, chinchilla, dog, ferret
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, february, november, may
House: farmhouse, tower, wooden, craftsman
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, lemonade, fanta
1. the tower house is the person who's birthday is in may##1
2. the wooden house is between the owner of the dog and the owner of the ferret##2
3. the tower house is the person drinking 7up##1
4. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
5. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
6. the person drinking lemonade is the owner of the dog##1
7. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
8. the farmhouse house is on the far right##1
9. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Pet   | chinchilla | ferret   | rabbit  | dog  |
| Birthday   | february    | may    | october      | november    |
| House   | craftsman | tower | wooden | farmhouse |
| Beverage     | fanta  | 7up       | almond-milk    | lemonade     |

