.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, april, november, october
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, brazilian, turkish, australian
The people have 4 different jobs:  videographer, musician, software-developer, designer
House: victorian, palace, ranch-style, townhouse
1. the townhouse house is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
2. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far right##1
3. the designer is the palace house##1
4. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
5. the australian is between the software-developer and the victorian house##2
6. the townhouse house is between the australian and the designer##2
7. the videographer is on the far right##1
8. the brazilian is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
9. the turkish is on the right of the musician##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Birthday         | october | april    | november  | february    |
| Nationality   | argentine      | brazilian  | australian  | turkish |
| Job           | designer      | software-developer       | musician      | videographer       |
| House         | palace    | townhouse | ranch-style | victorian |

