.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, tiparillo, bluemaster, bongani
4 different games are played: go, scrabble, backgammon, snooker
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, 7up, lemonade, juice
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, folk, salsa, ambient
1. the person drinking lemonade is the fan folk##1
2. the fan folk is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
3. the fan salsa is on the left of the fan folk##1
4. the fan folk is on the left of the fan metal##1
5. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
6. the person drinking 7up is the person playing snooker##1
7. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
8. the davidoff-smoker is between the person playing go and the person playing snooker##2
9. the person playing backgammon is between the bluemaster-smoker and the person drinking 7up##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Cigar        | tiparillo | bluemaster     | davidoff   | bongani     |
| Game       | scrabble   | go   | backgammon | snooker |
| Beverage         | soy-milk   | lemonade | juice       | 7up    |
| Music-Genre   | salsa    | folk | metal  | ambient    |

