 3. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the townhouse house##1
 4. the cape-cod house is on the far left##1
 5. the person who growsorchid is the person who's birthday is in december##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
 7. the person who growsbellflower is the person playing go##1
 8. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
 9. the person playing whist is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
10. the person playing mah-jongg is between the person who's birthday is in february and the person playing monopoly##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Game           | whist  | monopoly | mah-jongg     | go |
