 6. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 7. the person traveling to london is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
 8. the person traveling to venice is the person who's birthday is in january##1
 9. the pall-mall-smoker is between the egyptian and the person who's birthday is in june##2
10. the person who's birthday is in december is the malaysian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
