 3. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person who's birthday is in october and the modern house##2
 4. the person drinking water is the farmhouse house##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
 6. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the craftsman house##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in january is the palace house##1
 8. the person drinking milk is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
10. the person who's birthday is in october is the farmhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Pet   | bird | guinea-pig | fish  | pony  |
| Beverage   | coffee       | water   | soy-milk | milk    |
| Birthday   | january   | october   | december | april |
| House     | palace    | farmhouse   | craftsman    | modern  |

